I"§<p>ThumbTrak is a continuous one-handed thumb-on-fingers input technology. It allows the user to use the thumb to continuously input on fingers by tracking the position of the thumb using wearable motion sensing. It consists of a thumb-ring and a wristband. With ThumbTrak, the user is able to input on applications in one-hand, which demands continuously input capability, such as drawing and text entry applications.</p>
